description: This file is the entry point for a React-based web application. It imports essential React libraries, application components, and CSS. The code initializes the React DOM rendering process by attaching the React app to the DOM element with id 'root' and renders the App component within React.StrictMode for development checks.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for React rendering in the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders the React element tree into the DOM.
